  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "It's time to hit the town! Explore new worlds, customize accessories, and enjoy awesome mini-games, and collect six exclusive city pets with The Littlest Pet City Friends!\n\nThe Littlest Pet Shop: Friends series brings the party to you with a new cast of quirky pets and their best friends. Play tons of new mini-games and explore new towns with your favorite pets.\n\nWith enhanced multiplayer features, you can even double your fun by playing with your best friend! Venture on quests, deliver invitations, serve up ice cream, and style your pets as you get ready for the biggest Littlest Pet Shop party of the year. And be prepared for a few surprises along the way, like an all-new mystery pet that just might show up at your party!",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    }
